# Package Management Policy

## Pre-Approved Packages
✅ pandas, numpy, scipy, statsmodels, scikit-learn
✅ ECharts (via CDN in HTML only)

## Restricted Packages
❌ matplotlib, seaborn, plotly, bokeh, altair
❌ Any visualization library except ECharts
❌ chart.js, d3.js, recharts, victory

## Before Installing New Packages
1. Check if task can be done with approved packages
2. Explain why the new package is necessary
3. Provide ECharts-based alternatives
4. Wait for explicit user approval
5. Document the decision
